georeferenceSources: CRIA (Centro de Referência em Informação Ambiental)

locality: "Campos das Sete Lagôas". Fazenda Campininha, just north of Rio Moji-Guaçu. 9.7 km NNE of Padua Sales (About 27 km NW of city of Moji-Mirim).In recently plowed bround about 300 m south of fire tower.
name: Acrocomia hassleri (Barb.Rodr.) W.J.Hahn
habitat: Campo cerrado on upland (or occasionally forest). Open marsh on dense secondary forest along streams. Cut-over & burned campo cerrado.
